				<p>
					Joining is as simple as attending one Roll Session which is held from 7&ndash;10pm at the Claire Small Pool. Membership fee is $50, in the fall and $35 in the spring and Kayak Club is open to people of all skill levels and provides an environment for people to get together with others of the same interest for the love of kayaking and the outdoors. </p>
